::Shredder::

Shredder looks at Stingtra as she rolls behind the same rock as him, seconds 
before the rock is destroyed by Wrath's shots.

He growls, launching himself into the air and flipping towards Wrath. In 
mid-flip, he puts away one of his chain guns, pulling out a sword and 
swinging it at Wrath.
